sdp/logs/Verify_T-019_20260416T043834Z_1776324455.log:228:+- Implemented ST1-ST6 of the score-tree songwriting stack end to end: added `piece_commission.py`, `piece_brief.py`, `form_grammar.py`, `score_tree.py`, `recursive_composer.py`, `composition_gate.py`, `tracker_compiler.py`, and `piece_queue.py`; extended `repertoire_memory.py` to store structural score-tree summaries; and rewired `duet_composer.py` so tracker solo mode can commission a piece, build a complete score tree, gate it, compile it into tracker scenes, and precompose the next piece into a small persistent queue instead of treating the tracker as the composer.
